description: In case you find yourself cooking more during the pandemic, I am sharing with you how I mince my garlic and chop my onions and tomatoes. These three are usually my base ingredients in my cooking. I hope you find this video useful. It’s a casual shoot filmed by my ten-year-old nephew, Christian. I was helping his brother Charles with prepping his ingredients when I thought I should record it for you guys. I hope you enjoy! And if you have tips of your own, feel free to share!
